cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.SI, cs.LG 

The paper proposes a new deep CNN for detecting people looking at each other in videos, which is a computer vision task and falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces two new datasets for this task, which could potentially fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also applies the proposed method to social network analysis, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
